channel.description:

But on my old servers i had about 20-27 people on all the time. And the servers are both good. they have all skills. Skillcape emotes d claws. And its 317 if you were wondering.
And i cant think of anything i did different with my old server and my new one.
How can i get players online. (oh and i dont syi)
Thanks Please answer if you have the time. :D
